Great view of the city and well maintained
It's a very nice place to visit given its location. You get great views of the city with the beaches and the sea. The sculptures are amazing and very detailed. The whole vibe is calm and tranquil. Great spot to spend time gathering your thoughts and enjoy natural beauty.
