5.0 of 5 bubbles
Terrific Temple and best Da Nang bay views
Jan 2024 ‚Ä¢ Family
Lady Buddha is a magnificent temple complex located on a small peninsula north from Da Nang. It's easy reachable with taxi (Grab) with a few bucks 10-15 min ride.
Main star is the tallest Lady Buddha statue in all southeast Asia, but apart from it you can visit the Monastery complex with library, kitchen, etc... No fee entry.
From the Temple premises are amazing views of Da Nang bay with its high rises.
Count on around 1,5 - 2 hours for entire visit including transportation.
Written February 1, 2024
This review is the subjective opinion of a Tripadvisor member and not of Tripadvisor LLC. Tripadvisor performs checks on reviews as part of our industry-leading trust & safety standards. Read our transparency report to learn more.
