This is a "MUST SEE"
Dec 2022
If you ever visit Danang you must visit the Lady Buddha, perched on a hill at Son Tra, a little north of the city. We decided to walk there and get a taxi back, it is about 8 kms from Dragon Bridge but a nice walk along the beach and the winding road at the base of the mountain. It is easy to spend at least 2 hours here as there is so much to see nearby, including pagodas, temples. The statue is 67m tall and i believe the highest in Vietnam and you can see it from many parts of the city.
Written December 31, 2022
