Fabulous array of Bonsai.
Feb 2024 ‚Ä¢ Couples
The site is well maintained, plenty of shade and public toilets. Ladies can‚Äôt enter one of the areas in shorts, but they have wraps you can borrow to cover your knees. Great views across the water to the Da Nang skyline. There is a concession store selling ice creams and drinks at reasonable prices not inflated tourist prices. We took a grab from the Novotel Premium Han River Hotel for 155 VND. The driver said he would wait for 2 hours and then take us back. We were finished in 1 hour and he took us back to the Novotel for the same price.
