White marble Lady Buddha.
Nov 2023 ‚Ä¢ Family
We never heard about Lady Budha and temple for her amazed us. Such a big statue of white marble of Goddess / Lady Buddha facing sea is beautiful. We took numerous pictures around her . Atmosphere at afternoon time is pleasant . Place is quite neat and clean . You can spend about 1 hour relishing beautiful environs / sceneary here . However, lady Buddha statue is one of the highest in Danang / Vietnam which is visible from far of the places in Danang.
