Raymondale
Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia1,203 contributions
magnificent and solemn
Sep 2023 ‚Ä¢ Solo
i came here on 11 September when i stayed in da nang for two nights. lady buddha statue here is the tallest in vietnam, it is magnificent and solemn, it located at linh ung pagoda area, you can visit both in one day, you can see Da Nang city here also, beautiful city view. The statue stands facing the sea, with one hand praying and the other one holding a pitcher of nectar, as if she is blessing the fishermen who were reaching out to sea for a peaceful and successful crop. many tourists love to take pictures with lady buddha, as if doing so, will get protected by lady buddha, i am one of them too, haha. besides lady buddha, there is also a statue of laughing buddha, just standing in front of the lady buddha statue. both are important to Buddhists, if you came here, remember to pay respect to them, and also praying here.
Written October 4, 2023
